modules.description: Handles geometric transformations using affine matrices, including rotation, scaling, and translation. Operates on 2D points and vectors represented as tuples of floats. Enables precise manipulation of graphical elements in computer vision applications.

Converts Markdown strings to HTML using a build arrow, and applies Markdown conversion specifically to the content portion of a metadata-content pair. Works with strings and tuples containing metadata and document content. Useful for transforming blog posts or structured documents into HTML output.
